THE TEMPLATE LICENCE

This repository holds both the actual website (the thing that explains how to build websites) 
and an empty template that can be used as the basis for a website.

The actual website itself is not open source (see PERMISSIONS IN LIEU OF A LICENCE above).

The downloadable template is open source and is available under the MIT 
Licence below.




